<title>Capability Evolution Event Capture</title>

</head>
<body>

<h1>Capability Evolution Workflow</h1>

<p class=3D"small">
This form captures the workflow of events that evaluate and progress a <str=
ong>Capability Change Intent</strong> following the detection of system cha=
nges. Each event represents either a trigger or a structured decision point=
, guiding the progression of the proposed capability change to ensure it is=
 viable, strategically aligned and capable of delivering value.
</p>

<p class=3D"small">
<strong>Capability Change Intent:</strong> A clearly defined desired organi=
sational outcome or transformation that the enterprise aims to achieve. It =
represents the objective or goal that drives the workflow.
</p>

<p class=3D"small">
<strong>Event:</strong> An observable and measurable occurrence in the syst=
em or environment that can trigger activity or serve as a decision point fo=
r evaluating and progressing a Capability Change Intent. Events are the fun=
damental units that enable workflows to progress, refine or halt proposed c=
hanges. Depending on their role, events are classified as:
</p>

<ul class=3D"small">
    <li><strong>Triggering Event:</strong> A detectable change in system st=
ate that initiates a workflow, alert or action =E2=80=94 it starts the eval=
uation process, whether for automatic remediation or human consideration.</=
li>
    <li><strong>Controlling Event:</strong> A structured decision point wit=
hin a workflow that evaluates a Capability Change Intent to determine wheth=
er it should proceed, be refined or be halted =E2=80=94 it guides the workf=
low and may trigger the next stage.</li>
</ul>

<p class=3D"small">
In the ADT model, <strong>capability change intents</strong> define the tar=
get outcomes, while <strong>events</strong> are the observable occurrences =
that drive evaluation and progression. This distinction ensures that workfl=
ows remain transparent, accountable and strategically aligned, allowing ent=
erprises to allocate resources effectively across their transformation init=
iatives.
</p>

<form>

<!-- Event 1 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 1 =E2=80=94 Capability Change I=
ntent Validation &amp; Classification</div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"intent_id">Intent ID</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"intent_id" name=3D"intent_id" placeholde=
r=3D"Enter Intent ID">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"validation_date">Validation Date</label>
        <input type=3D"date" id=3D"validation_date" name=3D"validation_date=
">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"classification">Intent Classification</label>
        <select id=3D"classification" name=3D"classification">
            <option>Innovation</option>
            <option>Enhancement</option>
            <option>Maintenance</option>
            <option>Risk Mitigation</option>
            <option>Compliance</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"validator">Responsible Evaluator</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"validator" name=3D"validator" placeholde=
r=3D"Enter evaluator name">
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"initial_impact">Desired Outcome for Initial Impact Assessment=
</label>
<textarea id=3D"initial_impact" name=3D"initial_impact" rows=3D"3" placehol=
der=3D"Describe what should happen during this validation.">Confirm that th=
e capability change is valid, correctly classified and ready for evaluation=
 (e.g., classified as Innovation and assigned a priority).</textarea>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_1">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_1" name=3D"actual_outcome_1" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<!-- Event 2 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 2 =E2=80=94 Concept Development=
 / Prototyping</div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"concept_id">Concept ID</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"concept_id" name=3D"concept_id">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"prototype">Prototype Required</label>
        <select id=3D"prototype" name=3D"prototype">
            <option>Yes</option>
            <option>No</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"architecture_concept">Architecture Concept</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"architecture_concept" name=3D"architectu=
re_concept">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"concept_owner">Lead Architect / Designer</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"concept_owner" name=3D"concept_owner">
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"concept_description">Desired Outcome for Concept Description<=
/label>
<textarea id=3D"concept_description" name=3D"concept_description" rows=3D"3=
" placeholder=3D"Describe the intended outcome of concept development.">Det=
ermine if the proposed concept is feasible and aligns with the intent (e.g.=
, prototype demonstrates the feature successfully; architectural concept ap=
proved).</textarea>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_2">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_2" name=3D"actual_outcome_2" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<!-- Event 3 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 3 =E2=80=94 Strategic Feasibili=
ty Evaluation</div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"financial_feasibility">Financial Feasibility</label>
        <select id=3D"financial_feasibility" name=3D"financial_feasibility"=
>
            <option>Positive</option>
            <option>Marginal</option>
            <option>Negative</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"operational_feasibility">Operational Feasibility</lab=
el>
        <select id=3D"operational_feasibility" name=3D"operational_feasibil=
ity">
            <option>Feasible</option>
            <option>Requires Change</option>
            <option>Not Feasible</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"technical_feasibility">Technical Feasibility</label>
        <select id=3D"technical_feasibility" name=3D"technical_feasibility"=
>
            <option>Feasible</option>
            <option>Complex</option>
            <option>Not Feasible</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"strategic_alignment">Strategic Alignment</label>
        <select id=3D"strategic_alignment" name=3D"strategic_alignment">
            <option>High</option>
            <option>Moderate</option>
            <option>Low</option>
        </select>
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"feasibility_summary">Desired Outcome for Feasibility Summary<=
/label>
<textarea id=3D"feasibility_summary" name=3D"feasibility_summary" rows=3D"3=
" placeholder=3D"Summarise what a successful feasibility evaluation looks l=
ike.">Decide whether financial, operational and technical conditions suppor=
t proceeding (e.g., financially viable, technically feasible, aligned with =
strategic objectives).</textarea>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_3">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_3" name=3D"actual_outcome_3" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<!-- Event 4 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 4 =E2=80=94 Governance &amp; Qu=
ality Review</div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"architecture_review">Architecture Review Status</labe=
l>
        <select id=3D"architecture_review" name=3D"architecture_review">
            <option>Approved</option>
            <option>Conditional</option>
            <option>Rejected</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"risk_rating">Risk Rating</label>
        <select id=3D"risk_rating" name=3D"risk_rating">
            <option>Low</option>
            <option>Medium</option>
            <option>High</option>
            <option>Critical</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"compliance_status">Compliance Status</label>
        <select id=3D"compliance_status" name=3D"compliance_status">
            <option>Compliant</option>
            <option>Review Required</option>
            <option>Non-Compliant</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"review_board">Review Board</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"review_board" name=3D"review_board" plac=
eholder=3D"Enter review board name">
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"governance_notes">Desired Outcome for Governance and Quality<=
/label>
<textarea id=3D"governance_notes" name=3D"governance_notes" rows=3D"3" plac=
eholder=3D"Describe the expected governance outcomes.">Confirm initiative m=
eets quality, risk and compliance standards (e.g., architecture review appr=
oved, risk manageable, initiative cleared for portfolio planning).</textare=
a>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_4">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_4" name=3D"actual_outcome_4" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<!-- Event 5 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 5 =E2=80=94 Portfolio Planning<=
/div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"portfolio_priority">Portfolio Priority</label>
        <select id=3D"portfolio_priority" name=3D"portfolio_priority">
            <option>Low</option>
            <option>Medium</option>
            <option>High</option>
            <option>Strategic</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"portfolio_manager">Portfolio Manager</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"portfolio_manager" name=3D"portfolio_man=
ager" placeholder=3D"Enter portfolio manager name">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"resources">Estimated Resources</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"resources" name=3D"resources" placeholde=
r=3D"Enter resource estimates">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"delivery_window">Target Delivery Window</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"delivery_window" name=3D"delivery_window=
" placeholder=3D"Enter timeframe for delivery">
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"dependencies">Desired Outcome for Planning Intent</label>
<textarea id=3D"dependencies" name=3D"dependencies" rows=3D"3" placeholder=
=3D"Describe what a successful planning outcome looks like.">Determine prio=
rity, resource allocation and dependencies within the enterprise portfolio =
(e.g., initiative assigned high priority, resources allocated, dependencies=
 mapped).</textarea>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_5">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_5" name=3D"actual_outcome_5" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<!-- Event 6 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 6 =E2=80=94 Investment Decision=
</div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"investment_decision">Investment Decision</label>
        <select id=3D"investment_decision" name=3D"investment_decision">
            <option>Approved</option>
            <option>Deferred</option>
            <option>Rejected</option>
            <option>Further Investigation</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"investment_board">Investment Board</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"investment_board" name=3D"investment_boa=
rd" placeholder=3D"Enter investment board name">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"decision_date">Decision Date</label>
        <input type=3D"date" id=3D"decision_date" name=3D"decision_date">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"budget">Approved Budget</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"budget" name=3D"budget" placeholder=3D"E=
nter budget amount">
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"decision_rationale">Desired Outcome for Decision Rationale</l=
abel>
<textarea id=3D"decision_rationale" name=3D"decision_rationale" rows=3D"3" =
placeholder=3D"Describe expected rationale for investment decision.">Decide=
 whether to invest, defer or reject the initiative (e.g., investment approv=
ed with budget allocation, ready for transformation).</textarea>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_6">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_6" name=3D"actual_outcome_6" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<!-- Event 7 -->
<section>
<div class=3D"event-title">Intent for Event 7 =E2=80=94 Transformation Init=
iation</div>
<div class=3D"grid">
    <div>
        <label for=3D"program_id">Program / Project ID</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"program_id" name=3D"program_id" placehol=
der=3D"Enter program/project ID">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"program_manager">Program Manager</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"program_manager" name=3D"program_manager=
" placeholder=3D"Enter program manager name">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"start_date">Transformation Start Date</label>
        <input type=3D"date" id=3D"start_date" name=3D"start_date">
    </div>
    <div>
        <label for=3D"delivery_org">Delivery Organisation</label>
        <input type=3D"text" id=3D"delivery_org" name=3D"delivery_org" plac=
eholder=3D"Enter responsible delivery organisation">
    </div>
</div>

<label for=3D"implementation_overview">Desired Outcome for Transformation I=
ntent</label>
<textarea id=3D"implementation_overview" name=3D"implementation_overview" r=
ows=3D"3" placeholder=3D"Describe expected outcomes of transformation.">Del=
iver the intended capability successfully while tracking progress and outco=
mes (e.g., transformation program starts on schedule, delivery organisation=
 ready, KPIs defined).</textarea>

<label for=3D"actual_outcome_7">Actual Outcome</label>
<textarea id=3D"actual_outcome_7" name=3D"actual_outcome_7" rows=3D"2" plac=
eholder=3D"Record what actually occurred during this event."></textarea>
</section>

<button type=3D"submit">Submit Governance Workflow Record</button>

</form>


</body></html>
